name: Cheecoin
additional_notices: Kindly be aware that liquidity provided in Automated Market Maker platforms (eg. Uniswap, Sushiswap, Balancer) can be removed (also known as rug pulling), resulting in a collapse of available liquidity. Please exercise caution when trading! This notice is NOT directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder for our users.

description.en:
Over 4,100 cats and dogs are killed each day in shelters in the USA alone. Globally the numbers are much higher. Pets are abandoned or abused in record numbers since Covid – 19 and in many areas increasing. Our mission is to get that number to 0.

Cheecoin has partnered with different charities world-wide and works in tandem with their teams supporting and developing new rescue initiatives and community projects. Cheecoin also works with these organizations to build new facilities where surrendered, rescued, and abused animals can recover before finding their forever home.
